rows.label: qst202717_0010
rows.name: Not great...

rows.label: qst202717_0020
rows.name: What's not great?

rows.label: qst202717_0030
rows.name:
This ritual... It's entirely unlike the previous ones...
I can tell they really mean to summon something terrifying...

rows.label: qst202717_0040
rows.name: It not look any different to Tora...

rows.label: qst202717_0050
rows.name: Yeah, but... Somewhere inside, I can feel it.

rows.label: qst202717_0060
rows.name:
I believe Mei.
We need to stop them, and quick!

rows.label: qst202717_0070
rows.name:
Oi, you lot!
Run, now!

rows.label: qst202717_0080
rows.name: Leave here at once! Everyone!

rows.label: qst202717_0090
rows.name:
...Dammit!
What's going on there?!

rows.label: qst202717_0100
rows.name:
They've all been hypnotized.
They can't even hear us from here!

rows.label: qst202717_0110
rows.name: Who go there?

rows.label: qst202717_0120
rows.name:
We in middle of holy-holy rite!
No matter who you are, me no let you interfere!

rows.label: qst202717_0130
rows.name: Holy rite, my ass!

rows.label: qst202717_0140
rows.name:
If you don't stop this instant,
you'll all be killed!

rows.label: qst202717_0150
rows.name: That wonderful!

rows.label: qst202717_0160
rows.name:
That would be certain first step
to rebirth in new world!

rows.label: qst202717_0170
rows.name: Argh! Idiot... Too far up his own ass to listen.

rows.label: qst202717_0180
rows.name: Everyone, over there!

rows.label: qst202717_0190
rows.name: The prodigal daughter we'd been looking for!

rows.label: qst202717_0200
rows.name:
Sorry, old man, but
we'll be needing her back!

rows.label: qst202717_0210
rows.name:
Such action ill-advised.
Rite reach climax any moment now.

rows.label: qst202717_0220
rows.name:
Girl about to become offering for
His Dark Majesty!

rows.label: qst202717_0230
rows.name: I will not stand idly by!

rows.label: qst202717_0240
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo... You dead-set on stand in our way?
Want trouble, we happy to oblige.

rows.label: qst202717_0250
rows.name:
Your corpses also become offering to hasten
coming of new world!

rows.label: qst202717_0260
rows.name:
Feast eyes, mo!
Our Dark Majesty descend!

rows.label: qst202717_0270
rows.name: Mo-moooo!

rows.label: qst202717_0280
rows.name:
Come, Dark Majesty!
Make world your plaything, ripe for destru-

rows.label: qst202717_0290
rows.name: Mo-?!

rows.label: qst202717_0300
rows.name: Whuh-?!

rows.label: qst202717_0310
rows.name: Watch out!

rows.label: qst202717_0320
rows.name:
We'll have to kick that rampaging thing into the middle
of next week and get everyone to safety!

rows.label: qst202717_0330
rows.name:
Fully agree.
It might be a big job, though...

rows.label: qst202717_0340
rows.name: Someone's got to do it.

rows.label: qst202717_0350
rows.name:
If we leave it like this, it might not stop
till the whole world is in ruin...

rows.label: qst202717_0360
rows.name:
Ohoho... No need for alarm.
I am a Blade of Darkness, aren't I?

rows.label: qst202717_0370
rows.name:
My weapon arm has been raring to go
for a good long while now...

rows.label: qst202717_0380
rows.name:
With mine arms I will take you
exactly where you belong!

rows.label: qst202717_0390
rows.name: In hell, to rot!
